    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients aged between 18 and 85 years

          -  able to understand information

          -  affiliated to social security

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  active or suspected sepsis

          -  tumor around the knee

          -  previous partial or total knee replacement

